text: Burgadzhino () is a rural locality (a village) in Alegazovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 249 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 13 km from Alegazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Burgadzhino
